## Bladeburner.getAllBlackOps() method

Get an array of BlackOp objects with all name and required rank properties.

**Signature:**

```typescript
getAllBlackOps(): { name: string; rank: number }[];
```
**Returns:**

{ name: string; rank: number }\[\]

An array of BlackOp objects.

## Remarks

RAM cost: 0.4 GB

Returns an iterable array of objects, sorted by required rank. Each object contains the `.name` and `.rank` property of a Bladeburner Black Op.
